data.name: Label28.Text
data.value: Changes can be made here to the shipping address. For changes to be saved and used again, create a unique "Ship To ID" in the top field and edit address fields as necessary and alternate shipping address will be saved.

data.name: Label45.Text
data.value: For product drop shipped from an external vendor to a customer, create the Sales Order first, then create the PO from the SO in the Purchasing Module to ensure that the Sales Order and Purchase Order is linked for invoicing.
